The paper discusses the validation of agent-based models, which is a topic that falls under the category of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA). The paper also mentions the use of agent-based models in social networks (cs.SI), computer networks (cs.CE), and self-organizing networks (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a virtual overlay multi-agent system, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
